<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 00:56:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国将主导七国集团最后一天，教皇将主导人工智能讨论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-dominate-final-day-g7-pope-lead-ai-discussions-2024-06-14/</link><description>七国集团 (G7) 领导人将于周五在年度峰会上举行最后一天的会谈，中国是首要议题，随后教皇方济各历史性地露面讨论人工智能 (AI)。</description><pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 00:05:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-dominate-final-day-g7-pope-lead-ai-discussions-2024-06-14/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大公民承认窃取特斯拉商业机密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/canadian-national-pleads-guilty-stealing-tesla-trade-secrets-2024-06-13/</link><description>据美国司法部（DOJ）称，一名中国加拿大居民周四在纽约联邦法院承认窃取特斯拉电动汽车电池制造商业机密并密谋将其出售给便衣政府特工。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/canadian-national-pleads-guilty-stealing-tesla-trade-secrets-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>党魁称，故意帮助其他国家的加拿大议员必须被撤职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-lawmakers-who-knowingly-helped-other-nations-must-be-removed-party-leader-2024-06-13/</link><description>加拿大一个政党的领导人周四表示，一份关于一些议会成员充当其他国家代理人的情报报告令人担忧，必须将冒犯的议员撤职。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:26:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-lawmakers-who-knowingly-helped-other-nations-must-be-removed-party-leader-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美联储持谨慎态度，但日本央行呢？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-13/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 21:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>加纳债券持有人下周将与政府重新讨论债务重组</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/ghanas-bondholders-re-engage-government-next-week-debt-rework-2024-06-13/</link><description>四位消息人士告诉路透，加纳及其债券持有人将于下周重启谈判，商讨 130 亿美元国际债券的债务重组协议，此前该协议已于本周早些时候与官方债权人敲定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 20:37:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/africa/ghanas-bondholders-re-engage-government-next-week-debt-rework-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰泽连斯基称中国习近平告诉他不会向俄罗斯出售任何武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-zelenskiy-says-chinas-xi-told-him-he-will-not-sell-any-weapons-russia-2024-06-13/</link><description>泽连斯基周四表示，中国国家主席习近平在与乌克兰总统泽连斯基通电话时告诉乌克兰总统，中国不会向俄罗斯出售武器。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 20:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-zelenskiy-says-chinas-xi-told-him-he-will-not-sell-any-weapons-russia-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦表示中国大型银行对违反美国对俄罗斯制裁持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/yellen-says-larger-chinese-banks-wary-violating-us-sanctions-russia-2024-06-13/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四表示，她相信中国最大的银行注意到美国对俄罗斯的制裁，并且不想违反这些制裁，但她补充说，如果美国认为有必要，不排除采取行动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 18:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/yellen-says-larger-chinese-banks-wary-violating-us-sanctions-russia-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑对向俄罗斯国防部门供货的中国企业采取新行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-mulls-new-actions-against-china-firms-supplying-russia-defense-sector-2024-06-13/</link><description>美国国务院周四表示，美国正在考虑对一直向俄罗斯国防工业部门供货的中国公司采取进一步措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 18:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-mulls-new-actions-against-china-firms-supplying-russia-defense-sector-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员下周印度之行会见达赖喇嘛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-meet-dalai-lama-india-trip-next-week-2024-06-13/</link><description>共和党众议员迈克尔·麦考尔预计将在未来几天率领美国两党国会代表团前往印度，他和包括民主党前众议院议长南希·佩洛西在内的其他议员计划在那里会见西藏精神领袖达赖喇嘛。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 17:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmakers-meet-dalai-lama-india-trip-next-week-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>阿根廷市场为米莱在参议院和中国提振后欢呼“最好的一天”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/argentina-dollar-bonds-jump-senate-passing-reform-bill-china-swap-2024-06-13/</link><description>阿根廷市场周四上涨，参议院通过了一项庞大的法案，该法案对于自由主义总统哈维尔·米雷的经济改革计划至关重要，并与中国续签了货币互换贷款协议，投资者松了一口气。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:58:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/argentina-dollar-bonds-jump-senate-passing-reform-bill-china-swap-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲汽车制造商面临中国对欧盟关税的报复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-carmakers-exposed-any-chinese-retaliation-eu-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>欧盟委员会将从 7 月起对进口中国制造的电动汽车征收高达 38.1% 的额外关税，此举可能会遭到北京方面的报复。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-carmakers-exposed-any-chinese-retaliation-eu-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>耶伦：美国增长需要公共和私人投资，中国补贴过多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-says-public-private-investments-needed-sustain-us-growth-2024-06-13/</link><description>美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦周四表示，吸引私人资本的美国公共投资对于促进长期可持续和包容性增长至关重要，但警告说，中国大规模国家工业补贴的模式是世界不可接受的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/yellen-says-public-private-investments-needed-sustain-us-growth-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>美国预报员称拉尼娜天气有65%可能在7月至9月出现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/la-nina-weather-65-likely-develop-july-sept-says-us-forecaster-2024-06-13/</link><description>美国政府预报员周四表示，7 月至 9 月期间出现拉尼娜天气模式的可能性为 65%，其特点是太平洋寒冷。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:20:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/la-nina-weather-65-likely-develop-july-sept-says-us-forecaster-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>受规则和经济约束，欧盟在对华关税方面落后于美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bound-by-rules-economics-eu-trails-us-china-tariffs-2024-06-13/</link><description>欧盟计划对中国电动汽车加征关税，反映出其对北京的立场更加坚定，但与美国倾向于与中国彻底脱钩的更强硬立场相比，欧盟的计划有所不同。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bound-by-rules-economics-eu-trails-us-china-tariffs-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>贸易冲突恶化前法国烈酒出口大幅下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/french-spirits-exports-tumble-ahead-worsening-trade-conflict-2024-06-13/</link><description>行业游说团体周四表示，由于消费者继续削减支出，今年法国烈酒销售和出口大幅下降，并警告迫在眉睫的贸易壁垒可能会进一步损害该行业。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/french-spirits-exports-tumble-ahead-worsening-trade-conflict-2024-06-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>